00:26:53.409 --> 00:26:55.010
polyakn, goyim.

00:26:55.010 --> 00:26:56.343
letstns iz geven

00:26:56.343 --> 00:26:57.633
NIE KUPUJ OD ⟨ZYDA⟩

00:26:57.633 --> 00:26:59.360
iz geven far di milkhome.

00:26:59.417 --> 00:27:02.198
vos m'hot nit derlozn iz, az m'iz arayn tsu a yidn.

00:27:02.198 --> 00:27:03.208
di polyakn hobn zey gemakht.

00:27:03.551 --> 00:27:05.666
NIE KUPUJ OD ZYDOW, me zol nit koyfn bay yidn.

00:27:03.635 --> 00:27:04.254
lom-

00:27:05.576 --> 00:27:06.127
mh.

00:27:05.666 --> 00:27:07.421
az di yidn narn opet

00:27:07.449 --> 00:27:10.104
UNK ⟨ZYDO SZYKANY⟩ flegt dos zogn

00:27:10.104 --> 00:27:11.494
far di milkhome iz dos geven.

00:27:11.313 --> 00:27:14.863
lomir iberbaytn di tashme un redn a bisl vegn dem dernokh.

00:27:14.863 --> 00:27:15.696
a dank.
